secret.sharing

Class Encryptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • secret.sharing.Encryptor

  • public class Encryptor
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to encrypt data stream in advance Algorithm used in this class is: AES-128 / CBC + HMAC SHA3 Keyfactory: PBKDF2 with HMAC SHA1
    Author:
    Benjamin Weigl
